bug.short_desc: an internal error occurred during: "Refreshing repository configuration" (java.util.ConcurrentModificationException)

long_desc.thetext: Error when attaching Eclipse.org to Mylyn repositories. Dialog box with error: 'Refreshing repository configuration' has encountered a problem. An internal error occured during "Refreshing repository configuration". java.util.ConcurrentModificationException.

(In reply to comment #0) > Error when attaching Eclipse.org to Mylyn repositories. Dialog box with error: > 'Refreshing repository configuration' has encountered a problem. An internal > error occured during "Refreshing repository configuration". > java.util.ConcurrentModificationException.
Eclipse.org is already in the List of Mylyn repositories.
So can you give some more information what you want to do.
Please provide steps to reproduce the error and include all details from the error log if available.

Steps: 1. Start with a clean workspace on Eclipse 3.5 2. Create new Eclipse.org task 3. Open repository settings 4. Click finish

Steffen,
is this only with Eclipse 3.5 and Mylyn 3.8?
No, I don't think this is specific to Eclipse 3.5. I just happened to be testing on 3.5. It might be related to two repository configuration updates running concurrently but that's only a guess.
I create review https://git.eclipse.org/r/#/c/7107/ please verify

new patch set created in review https://git.eclipse.org/r/#/c/7107/
TaskRepository.isUpdating() is never used and TaskRepository.setUpdating(boolean) is only used with false so i remove the usage in BugzillaClientManager.repositoryChanged(...).new JobChangeAdapter() {...}.done(IJobChangeEvent)

It looks to me like the Bugzilla connector is triggering the configuration update twice - in the core and UI. I would like to only run one update and use scheduling rules for 3.9 (bug 389103) to prevent concurrent updates. Frank, I'll grab this bug for now.

I have pushed another review for the changes to the 3.8.x branch. The implementation changes are essentially the same but I retained the external interface to minimize changes: https://git.eclipse.org/r/#/c/7705/.
The changes were merged into master and the 3.8.x branch.
